  meanings
    entry
      definitions
        entry
          definition "A female deer; also used of similar animals such as antelope, (less commonly goat as nanny is also used)."
        entry
          definition "A female rabbit."
        entry
          definition "A female hare."
        entry
          definition "A female squirrel."
        entry
          definition "A female kangaroo."
      partOfSpeech noun
      synonyms (hind "blue flyer")
